{"tid":2312964,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解佐助同小櫻會變成一對? 點解會揀佢做女主角?","createTime":"2020-12-05T11:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T18:04:28.000Z","uid":3189,"like":106,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb869433ae413c82ef1099814175c43fde6d9d2","tid":2312964,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"唔覺好奇怪咩<br />\n港女櫻由頭到尾都係自作多情<br />\n劇情上佐助一直對港女櫻都冇乜表示<br />\n但又唔知點解最尾硬湊變成一對<br />\n一啲愛情基礎都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而大波田同嗚人嗰種互動一直都有係劇情表現出嚟<br />\n去到佩恩嗰度<br />\n大波田根本升上女角之位<br />\n佢地變成一對好合理<br />\n<br />\n作用上<br />\n嗰隻港女除咗喊同大叫嗚門/佐助之類仲有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打鬥戲份得同千代婆婆VS蠍嗰場可以吹奏吓<br />\n其他劇情嚟講係可有可無+好想打鳩港女櫻<br />\n真係希望最後死嗰個係港女櫻而唔係寧次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQAP3FE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQAP3FE.png&h=68081af2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2ba2d0173fe2932e73a9d1bf99c1855e3c2e3ea","tid":2312964,"uid":309553,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"打贏做火影<br />\n打輸娶小櫻"},{"pid":"778a81760a233e9a2f9b17516d4165ce720321a6","tid":2312964,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚嗚"},{"pid":"c9e83e18d84eee7a9f5d725ad08a54c5e610a0e7","tid":2312964,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ba2d0173fe2932e73a9d1bf99c1855e3c2e3ea","tid":2312964,"uid":309553,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"打贏做火影<br />\n打輸娶小櫻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d980d62e7fe2db31d8c316e83ce14e3bf08913","tid":2312964,"uid":220236,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好撚憎佢 阻鳩住佐助"},{"pid":"b32aef840c06